title: New Orders of Architectural Terra Cotta for United States
notes:
Data Are From Reports Of 16 Manufacturers Who Produced Over 99 Per Cent Of The Total Architectural Terra Cotta Made In 1929. Source: U.S. Bureau Of The Census, "Terra Cotta" Releases Of January 28, 1932 And Following.

This NBER data series m06035 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 6 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter06.html.
